            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Striatal</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Neuron-Packing Density</ENAMEX> and Neuron
            Number
            Neurons were counted using the 3-dimensional
            counting software of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Williams</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Rakic</ENAMEX> [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">24</TIMEX>]. A series
            of <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">six</NUMEX> contiguous counting boxes (each <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">40 x 65 x 20 Î¼m</NUMEX>)
            aligned in a <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">3 x 2 matrix</NUMEX> were placed randomly within
