            <NUMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">20 Î¼m</NUMEX>) was chosen to minimize sampling variance by
            ensuring an equitable sampling of striatal patch and
            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">matrix</ENAMEX>. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">Two</NUMEX> of these large fields were counted in each
