            by <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">5</NUMEX> sections from the previous series. The
            correlations among the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">three</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">estimations</ENAMEX> ranged from
            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">.95</NUMEX> to <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">.99</NUMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">P < .05</ENAMEX>), indicating a high degree of
            reliability for this dependent variable.
            We assessed reliability of our estimates of neuronal
