            <ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">neuron</ENAMEX> number in the same <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">10</NUMEX> brains above. The
            intra-<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">observer</ENAMEX> correlation for this measure was <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">.81</NUMEX> (P
            <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">< .05</NUMEX>), which is similar to the reliability seen in
