            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Regression Analysis of Trait Values</ENAMEX>
            The unadjusted striatal estimates vary to a large
            extent as a result of variation in total brain weight.
            However, one of our goals in this study is to map QTLs
            with relatively intense effects on the striatum. For
            this reason we also have corrected all of the
            parameters used in the mapping analysis for variation
            in brain weight using linear regression analysis. We
            have mapped data with and without compensation for
            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">variance</ENAMEX> in brain weight. The corrected values are
            referred to as residuals.
          
        
        
